The LICENSE.md in this directory is the Stability AI Community License Agreement (Last
Updated: July 5, 2024), the licence family Stability AI applies across its open-weight
Stable Audio releases.

It was first drafted from the publicly-readable licence text on the sibling
stabilityai/stable-audio-open-1.0 model card, since stable-audio-3-medium/-small-sfx/
-small-music are gated on Hugging Face and were not reachable without authentication at
the time this tool was built. generate.py automatically re-fetches and overwrites this
LICENSE.md from the actual selected model's own repo immediately after the first
successful authenticated model load - this has since happened for real (2026-07-13, AUDIOFORGE
pre-flight run, `stabilityai/stable-audio-3-medium`): the file now on disk is the genuine
repo-specific LICENSE.md, confirmed identical in substance to the earlier best-effort
draft (only raw-text formatting differs - smart quotes, no markdown headers).
